name: Suburbia #1
description:
This is the 1st of a 4 pictures set about empty spaces in a crowded word.
You can feel the human absence even in a people packed suburb.
Nobody is really here, life of inhabitants are flowing elsewhere.
The set has been shot on a digital reflex camera with a vintage lens.
Bringing back objects from the past, such as these lenses of the '60s / '70s is one of the point of the project. 
These images of abandoned places are taken with forgotten lenses, lost in time and space.
So the observer and the observed acquire both a new meaning, far from their creators.
